    { '@type': 'Question', 'name': `What is the best self-care gift for women in 2026?`, 'acceptedAnswer': { '@type': 'Answer', 'text': `The Wireless LED Face Mask ($69.99) is our top pick â it combines red, blue, and infrared light therapy in a cordless design. It scored 79/100 in our testing.` } },
